{
  "stem": "11801.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So she used to take me to these soup kitchens or you know, take me with her to-- she'd take me with her to wherever she was going.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she felt very much at home with the survivors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Those were her friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I finally said, this is not where I want to be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This is not a reality that I want to handle, certainly not at that point in my life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, I was dreaming of other things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And for better or worse, I, I didn't want to know about these things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she stopped taking me there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she decided she had to make more money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father did send some money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But in those days, it, it took time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It didn't-- it didn't happen overnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so she got a job as a, as a cook and housekeeper with a family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she used to sneak a little food out for me and-- so that we'd. you know-- she could give me a meal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't spend the day with her and not eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] eventually, I guess, my German came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or a little bit of it came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took, took a while, though.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, it didn't happen overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just reconnecting with your mother, it's not like picking up the pieces that you, you know, put aside yesterday.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not like going away to a summer camp or to college and being away from home for a month, or a year, or two years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, this was seven years during my growing years, and in very abnormal, unusual times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we'd both had very different experiences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we really couldn't dialogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not equipped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have the-- I wouldn't even call it vocabulary.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
